Minister of Humanitarian Affairs, Disaster Management and Social Development, Sadiya Umar Farouk, has renewed her membership of All Progressives Congress (APC) in Zamfara State.
Farouq revalidated her membership as a staunch member at the APC headquarters in Gusau at the weekend.
She was thereafter presented with her membership card by the state Caretaker Chairman, Lawal Kaura.